_:N975ab36c02ce463786e86b729866e7db <http://schema.org/description> "Office of the Public Guardian (OPG) helps people in England and Wales to stay in control of decisions about their health and finance and make important decisions for others who cannot decide for themselves. OPG is an executive agency, sponsored by the Ministry of Justice ." .
